docs.lead_paragraph: The market yesterday showed a much steadier tendency than that which prevailed in the two preceding sessions, and although rates slumped in the forenoon, in keeping with weakness in the foreign centres, a later rally made up some of the earlier losses. Scandinavians were a feature, advancing beyond Tuesday's levels.
